metatags.og:description: Directed by Jong-hyuk Lee.  With Jung-ah Yum, Jin-hee Ji, Ji-ru Sung, Seung-woo Cho. A serial killer named Shin-Hyun gives himself up to police. He confesses to committing a series of particularly horrifying murders of exclusively female victims. He is imprisoned, awaiting the death sentence for his crimes. Yet the killings do not stop.
